@startuml
state PowerOn
state ReadyToUse
state AlarmActive
state FalseAlarm
state Normal

[*] PowerOn --> ReadyToUse: CheckEverythingWorking

ReadyToUse --> Reset: User_Reset
ReadyToUse --> Activate: User_Activate
ReadyToUse --> Off: User_TurnOff

Activate --> AlarmActive: StartMonitoring
AlarmActive --> FalseAlarm: SensorFalseAlarm
AlarmActive --> Normal: ContinueMonitoring

FalseAlarm --> AlarmActive: TimeEnds
Normal --> PowerOn: SystemProblemDuringStartup

Off --> PowerOn: SystemShutdown
Reset --> ReadyToUse: SystemReset

state PasswordInput
[*] Normal --> PasswordInput: User_EntersPassword
PasswordInput --> Normal: PasswordCorrect
PasswordInput --> Off: PasswordIncorrect
@enduml
